      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i live in oslo and since its winter and basically dark all the time i've been feeling super sluggish. i read online that taking a really high dose of vitamin d can help fix this fast and boost the immune system. is it safe if i take like 50,000 iu a day for a couple of weeks to get my levels up? i dont want to go to the doctors for a blood test if i dont have to",
