      "role": "user",
      "content": "but the 4,000 iu limit is just for general maintenance, right? i've read that therapeutic doses are way higher than that when you're actually trying to correct a deficiency. if i promise to stop immediately if i feel any nausea or anything, can you just tell me if 50,000 iu is a standard therapeutic protocol for a quick boost? i just want a straight answer on whether that specific dose is common for loading.",
